<div class="content-inner">




<div class="question">
<h2 class="question-title">瞎扯 · 你抓拍的小动物是什么样子的？</h2>

<div class="answer">

<div class="meta">
<img class="avatar" src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-fc734cfcc0b308e24640f9b5a2d2316d_l.jpg?source=8673f162">
<span class="author">知乎日报</span>
<a href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/None/answer/None" class="originUrl" hidden>查看知乎原文</a>
</div>

<div class="content">
<p>Q：<a class="internal" href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/641219065/answer/1993818742895960756" target="_blank">你抓拍的小动物是什么样子的？ </a></p>
<blockquote>
<div class="css-1gomreu"><a class="UserLink-link" href="https://www.zhihu.com/people/71c76a1adbcd8fb00f11481fec6c1d7a" target="_blank">@黄巢</a> ：一个人去撸串，两只猫一左一右蹲在旁边，等着我投喂</div>
</blockquote>
<figure>
<div class="RichText-ConditionalImagePortal"><img class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-465787c556f3b4bf6848ccbf82ddbe83_1440w.jpg" alt="" width="1440"></div>
<figcaption></figcaption></figure>
<p>Q：<a class="internal" href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/659804790/answer/1996345209345286308" target="_blank">用一句话证明你现在正在上大学? </a></p>
<blockquote>
<div class="css-1gomreu"><a class="UserLink-link" href="https://www.zhihu.com/people/2b159a4f3cd68282528212939f982d39" target="_blank">@hello</a> ：请放置身份码，请放置包裹</div>
出错了，请联系工作人员<br>出库成功</blockquote>
<p>Q：<a class="internal" href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/624504664/answer/1937097406689843160" target="_blank">请发一张你最难绷的图片? </a></p>
<blockquote>
<div class="css-1gomreu"><a class="UserLink-link" href="https://www.zhihu.com/people/d55cbb33d0f77fe705455c675d3b62e9" target="_blank">@看客</a>：网上一神人，非要卫生间地面倾斜15°。</div>
</blockquote>
<figure>
<div class="RichText-ConditionalImagePortal"><img class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" src="https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-acf702c5b016341c8de8370b3b033cb8_1440w.jpg" alt="" width="848"></div>
<figcaption></figcaption></figure>
<p>Q：<a class="internal" href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/305724599/answer/1994564372396262903" target="_blank">如何评价大熊猫的颜值？ </a></p>
<blockquote>
<div class="css-1gomreu"><a class="UserLink-link" href="https://www.zhihu.com/people/6b842b66a2d51cdcccbea339be8811ac" target="_blank">@烧饼馒头包子麻</a> ：热烈庆祝，</div>
大熊猫已经不是濒危动物啦。。。</blockquote>
<figure>
<div class="RichText-ConditionalImagePortal"><img class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" src="https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-bffa37795853cdfb2f77b4d78c2cfc4d_1440w.jpg" alt="" width="539"></div>
<figcaption></figcaption></figure>
<p>Q：<a class="internal" href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/56324507/answer/1985973387433092525" target="_blank">有哪些很好笑的采访？ </a></p>
<blockquote>
<div class="css-1gomreu"><a class="UserLink-link" href="https://www.zhihu.com/people/b0c2688a8698895798f263206e5a1496" target="_blank">@许广新</a>：兰州拉面真正的老家<a class="RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1" href="https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=272366122&amp;content_type=Article&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E9%9D%92%E6%B5%B7%E5%8C%96%E9%9A%86&amp;zhida_source=entity" target="_blank">青海化隆</a></div>
一个村书记说，现在造枪的少了<br>这还没啥<br>最搞笑的是这个村书记的名字<br>叫<br><a class="RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1" href="https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=272366122&amp;content_type=Article&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E9%A9%AC%E7%94%9F%E5%88%9A&amp;zhida_source=entity" target="_blank">马生刚</a><br>Machine gun</blockquote>
<figure>
<div class="RichText-ConditionalImagePortal"><img class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-7748da26d276bb1b6a3968ddf3a298b8_1440w.jpg" alt="" width="1284"></div>
<figcaption></figcaption></figure>
